<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_8dc6bfdcb15a.aspx"><b>终南</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson8dc6bfdcb15a">
<p>终南何有？有条有梅。君子至止，锦衣狐裘。颜如渥丹，其君也哉！<br />终南何有？有纪有堂。君子至止，黻衣绣裳。佩玉将将，寿考不忘！</p>
